mcwm - Messy Code Window Manager
-------------

A lightweight, fun window manager. Made for X

Requirements
-------------
In order to build dwm you need the Xlib header files.

Installation
-------------

in your shell

$ git clone https://github.com/messycode0/mcwm.git

enter into it

$ make 
then
$ sudo make install

in your ~/.xinitrc (make it if missing) 
put in 

exec mcwm

Configuration
-------------
The configuration of dwm is done by creating a custom config.h
and (re)compiling the source code.

No Config.yaml files or whatever... you edit the source code. like a boss. 
